<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Due to a check on both $param2 and $param3 being null in the constructor of Zend_Pdf_Page, the parameters passed from Zend_Pdf::newPage can never work with a Zend_Pdf_Page object parameter (used this way to use an existing page as a 'template').</p>

<p>This can be triggered by:</p>

<p>$pdf = new Zend_Pdf();
$template = new Zend_Pdf_Page(Zend_Pdf_Page::SIZE_A4);
$page = $pdf-&gt;newPage($template); //error is thrown</p>

<p>I believe the manual states this is possible.</p>

